  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The specific aims of the proposed study are to evaluate the effectiveness and
      cost-effectiveness of providing monetary incentives to therapists as a method to improve
      implementation of evidence-based treatments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
